Directing customers to Subscription through Financial app behaviour analysis¶

Goal of the project¶

There is a app manufacturing company which created two version of an app that is free and premium. Company want to know how many users use the premium version and how many use the free version.The company made the premium version free for 24 hours.We have to find how many users downloaded the premium version of the app
